{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HyDupViUTQ1xM3tEmBKWKT","type":"tool_result","content":"total 2556\ndrwxr-xr-x. 1 root    root      28 Mar 17 02:45 .\ndrwxrwx---. 1 default root      45 Mar 17 02:45 ..\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root    root 2614933 Sep 18  2023 h2-2.2.224.jar\n---\ntotal 2480\ndrwxrwx---. 1 default root      24 Mar 17 02:45 .\ndrwxrwx---. 1 default root      45 Mar 17 02:45 ..\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root    root 2539408 Mar 17 02:45 roster.war\n---\ntotal 8\ndrwxrwxr-x. 1 default root  26 Mar 17 02:45 .\ndrwxrwxr-x. 1 default root  22 Mar 16 09:48 ..\n-rw-rw-r--. 1 root    root 214 Mar 17 02:45 keystore.xml\n-rw-rw-r--. 1 default root  97 Mar 16 09:48 open-default-port.xml","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"98f0c157-25c8-4522-ad5d-c073f4a9b639","uuid":"506b83f2-5232-46a9-8e54-4083482e68a4"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VDJt4PMJc9BtMX31Wpz6FD","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"H2 jar is at `/opt/ol/wlp/usr/servers/defaultServer/lib/h2-2.2.224.jar`. The `${server.config.dir}` should be `/opt/ol/wlp/usr/servers/defaultServer`. The fileset `dir=\"${server.config.dir}/lib\"` should resolve to `/opt/ol/wlp/usr/servers/defaultServer/lib`. This should work.\n\nBut wait, the error mentions `DefaultDataSource` not `RosterDS`. This means there's another datasource lookup happening. Perhaps the persistence.xml doesn't match correctly. Also, let me check if the problem is that `configDropins/defaults/` has generated additional configuration.\n\nThe error `\"Searched in: []\"` is key - it means the fileset resolved to empty. This could be a permissions issue, since the file is owned by root but Liberty runs as default user. But wait, we're running as root now...\n\nActually, the issue might be that the liberty:deploy copied the server.xml but didn't use MY server.xml. The build process uses `liberty:create liberty:install-feature liberty:deploy` which creates the server from the plugin config. Let me check if the liberty maven plugin is configured to use my server.xml. I specified `src/main/liberty/config/server.xml` which is the default location - so it should be used.\n\nWait, looking at the output server.xml again, it IS using my content but it looks modified. It has `RosterDS` instead of `rosterDS`. That's odd. Actually - looking again, the server.xml in the container shows `jdbc/RosterDS` but my server.xml has `jdbc/rosterDS`. This means the liberty plugin may be generating its own. Let me check by looking at how liberty plugin creates the server.xml:\n\nThe real problem is clearer now:\n1. The H2 driver error references `DefaultDataSource` not `RosterDS` - there may be a default persistence.xml being used\n2. The JNDI names might not match\n\nLet me fix the approach. Instead of using the Liberty Maven Plugin (which has its own opinions), let me use a simpler approach: download Liberty directly and set it up manually in the Docker build:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1036,"cache_read_input_tokens":105158,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1036,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1383},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"98f0c157-25c8-4522-ad5d-c073f4a9b639","uuid":"cee60412-fa61-4170-b76a-bffff42322fa"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VDJt4PMJc9BtMX31Wpz6FD","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01FkYPsgNagRqq7MZZZr5aF3","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__persistence__roster__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml","old_string":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<server description=\"Roster Jakarta EE Application\">\n    <featureManager>\n        <feature>jakartaee-10.0</feature>\n    </featureManager>\n\n    <httpEndpoint id=\"defaultHttpEndpoint\"\n                  httpPort=\"8080\"\n                  httpsPort=\"9443\"\n                  host=\"*\" />\n\n    <!-- H2 Database Library -->\n    <library id=\"h2Lib\">\n        <fileset dir=\"${server.config.dir}/lib\" includes=\"h2-*.jar\"/>\n    </library>\n\n    <!-- DataSource for H2 in-memory database -->\n    <dataSource id=\"rosterDS\" jndiName=\"jdbc/rosterDS\" type=\"javax.sql.DataSource\">\n        <jdbcDriver libraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n        <properties.generic URL=\"jdbc:h2:mem:roster;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1;DB_CLOSE_ON_EXIT=FALSE\"\n                            user=\"sa\"\n                            password=\"\"/>\n    </dataSource>\n\n    <!-- Application deployment -->\n    <webApplication id=\"roster\" location=\"roster.war\" contextRoot=\"/\">\n        <classloader commonLibraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n    </webApplication>\n</server>","new_string":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<server description=\"Roster Jakarta EE Application\">\n\n    <featureManager>\n        <feature>jakartaee-10.0</feature>\n    </featureManager>\n\n    <httpEndpoint id=\"defaultHttpEndpoint\"\n                  httpPort=\"8080\"\n                  httpsPort=\"9443\"\n                  host=\"*\" />\n\n    <!-- H2 Database Library -->\n    <library id=\"h2Lib\">\n        <fileset dir=\"${server.config.dir}/lib\" includes=\"h2-*.jar\"/>\n    </library>\n\n    <!-- DataSource for H2 in-memory database -->\n    <dataSource id=\"rosterDS\" jndiName=\"jdbc/rosterDS\">\n        <jdbcDriver libraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n        <properties.generic URL=\"jdbc:h2:mem:roster;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1;DB_CLOSE_ON_EXIT=FALSE\"\n                            user=\"sa\"\n                            password=\"\"/>\n    </dataSource>\n\n    <!-- Default DataSource (same as rosterDS, for JPA default persistence unit) -->\n    <dataSource id=\"DefaultDataSource\" jndiName=\"jdbc/DefaultDataSource\">\n        <jdbcDriver libraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n        <properties.generic URL=\"jdbc:h2:mem:roster;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1;DB_CLOSE_ON_EXIT=FALSE\"\n                            user=\"sa\"\n                            password=\"\"/>\n    </dataSource>\n\n    <!-- Application deployment -->\n    <webApplication id=\"roster\" location=\"roster.war\" contextRoot=\"/\">\n        <classloader commonLibraryRef=\"h2Lib\"/>\n    </webApplication>\n</server>"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1036,"cache_read_input_tokens":105158,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1036,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1383},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"98f0c157-25c8-4522-ad5d-c073f4a9b639","uuid":"1943ea0c-6c29-4ebb-9f4d-c261dbfd72f1"}
